WEBVTT

00:00.368 --> 00:00.534
.

00:00.568 --> 00:01.402
announcer:
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:02.436 --> 00:03.704
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES

00:03.737 --> 00:05.206
ARE CONSIDERED
ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:05.239 --> 00:07.408
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:07.441 --> 00:09.410
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:09.443 --> 00:11.045
ARE MEMBERS OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:11.079 --> 00:13.081
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:13.114 --> 00:15.616
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:15.649 --> 00:17.085
- DETECTIVE CASSIDY,

00:17.118 --> 00:18.286
YOU SPENT
THREE YEARS UNDERCOVER

00:18.319 --> 00:20.221
AS MUSCLE
FOR A PIMP NAMED BART GANZEL.

00:20.254 --> 00:21.622
ISN'T THAT RIGHT?

00:21.655 --> 00:24.292
- YEAH. MY SEVERANCE WAS
TWO BULLETS IN THE CHEST.

00:24.325 --> 00:27.128
- CASSIDY, CAN WE PRACTICE
ANSWERING THE QUESTIONS

00:27.161 --> 00:28.196
IN THE ORDER I ASK THEM?

00:28.229 --> 00:30.731
- OKAY. SURE, COUNSELOR.

00:30.764 --> 00:32.233
- ALL RIGHT.

00:32.266 --> 00:35.436
IN THE COURSE OF YOUR EMPLOYMENT
WITH MR. GANZEL,

00:35.469 --> 00:39.307
DID YOU MEET A PROSTITUTE
NAMED CARISSA GIBSON?

00:39.340 --> 00:41.242
- WE REALLY NEED
TO REHASH ALL THAT? HUH?

00:41.275 --> 00:44.445
HEY, GANZEL CONFESSED
TO MURDER ON TAPE.

00:44.478 --> 00:45.713
- YEAH, WELL,
HIS NEW ATTORNEY IS CONTESTING

00:45.746 --> 00:47.281
THE TAPE'S ADMISSIBILITY.

00:47.315 --> 00:49.183
- YEAH? AND HOW'S THAT
MY PROBLEM?

00:49.217 --> 00:50.284
- LOOK, I WISH
YOU WEREN'T MY WITNESS.

00:50.318 --> 00:51.785
YOU WISH
YOU WEREN'T MY WITNESS.

00:51.819 --> 00:56.090
BUT HERE WE ARE,
SO LET'S GET THROUGH THIS.

00:56.124 --> 00:58.092
- ASK AWAY, COUNSELOR.

00:58.126 --> 00:59.660
- YEAH,
I'LL AMTRAK DOWN SUNDAY.

00:59.693 --> 01:03.697
MAYBE TAKE ZARA
TO THE NATIONAL ZOO.

01:03.731 --> 01:05.566
YEAH, I'LL HOLD.

01:05.599 --> 01:07.101
- TRY THE BUS, NICK.

01:07.135 --> 01:08.802
NEW YORK TO D.C., 20 BUCKS.

01:08.836 --> 01:10.538
- YOU HAVE NO STOPS
FOR BATHROOM BREAKS.

01:10.571 --> 01:13.641
- SEE, THAT'S WHY
I DON'T TAKE TRIPS WITH WOMEN.

01:13.674 --> 01:14.875
- OH, I DIDN'T KNOW
THAT WAS VOLUNTARY.

01:14.908 --> 01:16.644
- [chuckles]
- GO HOME, MUNCH.

01:16.677 --> 01:18.346
THERE'LL BE BAD GUYS
TO CATCH TOMORROW.

01:18.379 --> 01:19.647
- UH, WHO ARE YOU,

01:19.680 --> 01:20.881
AND WHAT HAVE YOU DONE
WITH DETECTIVE BENSON?

01:20.914 --> 01:22.483
- TAKIN' THE NIGHT OFF.

01:22.516 --> 01:24.118
- WITH THE CAPTAIN
ON VACATION?

01:24.152 --> 01:25.419
DON'T WORRY ABOUT US,
WE'RE FINE.

01:25.453 --> 01:27.755
WE'LL CARRY ON.
- MARIA, ALL RIGHT, JUST LISTEN.

01:27.788 --> 01:29.490
HEY--

01:29.523 --> 01:30.724
YEAH, I DON'T SEE
HOW IT CAN CONFLICT

01:30.758 --> 01:32.193
WITH HER SCHEDULE, MARIA.

01:32.226 --> 01:33.494
SHE'S SIX.

01:33.527 --> 01:35.363
WELL...

01:35.396 --> 01:37.231
I'LL CALL YOU LATER.

01:37.265 --> 01:39.267
[hangs up phone]

01:39.300 --> 01:40.534
CAN I HELP YOU?

01:40.568 --> 01:42.836
- I HOPE SO.

01:42.870 --> 01:44.338
I WAS RAPED.

01:44.372 --> 01:46.740
BY A COP.

01:46.774 --> 01:49.777
- SHE SAYS CASSIDY RAPED HER?

01:49.810 --> 01:51.245
OUR CASSIDY?

01:51.279 --> 01:52.280
- SHE SAYS
IT WAS FOUR YEARS AGO.

01:52.313 --> 01:53.547
HE WAS UNDERCOVER
WITH SOME PIMP.

01:53.581 --> 01:55.149
NEVER SAW HIM AGAIN

01:55.183 --> 01:56.217
TILL SHE RECOGNIZED HIS PICTURE
IN THE PAPER

01:56.250 --> 01:57.685
ABOUT THE GANZEL TRIAL.

01:57.718 --> 02:00.154
- WELL, THAT'S ONE HELL
OF A COINCIDENCE.

02:00.188 --> 02:02.656
CASSIDY'S GETTING READY
TO TESTIFY AGAINST GANZEL,

02:02.690 --> 02:05.226
AND THIS WOMAN APPEARS,
MAKING ACCUSATIONS.

02:05.259 --> 02:07.328
- ALL RIGHT, WE KNOW
HE CROSSED SOME LINES.

02:07.361 --> 02:09.363
- YOU WERE HERE WHEN GANZEL
DRUGGED OUR CAPTAIN,

02:09.397 --> 02:10.664
PUT A DEAD HOOKER
IN HIS BED.

02:10.698 --> 02:12.233
- YOU MEAN CARISSA:

02:12.266 --> 02:13.801
THE HOOKER
CASSIDY HAD AN AFFAIR WITH?

02:13.834 --> 02:15.603
- YEAH, THAT'S WHY
HE WAS BUSTED DOWN TO UNI,

02:15.636 --> 02:17.338
AND WORKS NIGHTS
AT A BRONX COURTHOUSE.

02:17.371 --> 02:18.839
HE'S PAID THE PRICE.

02:18.872 --> 02:20.441
- OKAY, SO WHAT DO WE DO, HMM?

02:20.474 --> 02:21.942
TELL THIS WOMAN
TO TAKE A HIKE?

02:21.975 --> 02:23.511
- THERE'S PROTOCOL.

02:23.544 --> 02:26.447
WE HAVE TO NOTIFY IAB
OR OUR COMMANDING OFFICER.

02:26.480 --> 02:28.316
WE'LL TRY CRAGEN FIRST.

02:28.349 --> 02:31.319
- ON A FISHING BOAT
OFF BIMINI?

02:31.352 --> 02:33.254
- RULES ARE RULES.

02:34.822 --> 02:37.825
I DON'T WANT YOU
ENJOYING THIS TOO MUCH, OKAY?

02:37.858 --> 02:39.360
- [mouth full] COMING!
HOLD ON A SECOND.

02:39.393 --> 02:42.496
[lock clacks]

02:42.530 --> 02:44.332
WHAT ARE YOU GUYS DOING HERE?
- NUMBNUTS.

02:44.365 --> 02:46.300
DON'T YOU ASK WHO IT IS
BEFORE YOUR OPEN THE DOOR?

02:46.334 --> 02:47.535
- I THOUGHT YOU WERE
MY THAI FOOD.

02:47.568 --> 02:49.403
- WE NEED TO TALK.

02:49.437 --> 02:51.205
- NOW. CAN WE COME IN?

02:51.239 --> 02:52.906
- IT'S NOT A REAL GOOD TIME
RIGHT NOW, GUYS.

02:52.940 --> 02:54.375
- BRI--
- I GOT THIS.

02:54.408 --> 02:55.409
IT'S TAKEN CARE OF.

02:55.443 --> 02:57.378
- YOU HAVE COMPANY?
- YEAH.

02:57.411 --> 02:58.212
IT'S YOUR SISTER.

02:58.246 --> 02:59.713
YOU SHOULD HAVE TOLD ME
SHE SNORES.

02:59.747 --> 03:01.349
I'LL CALL YOU TOMORROW.

03:01.382 --> 03:04.885
- HEY, NEED CHANGE?

03:04.918 --> 03:06.754
- LIV?

03:06.787 --> 03:10.958
- HEY, GUYS.

03:14.928 --> 03:17.898
[edgy pop music]

04:02.676 --> 04:02.943
.

04:02.976 --> 04:03.544
- IAB CALLED ME AT 6:00 A.M.

04:04.945 --> 04:06.380
- WE TRIED
TO GIVE YOU A HEADS UP,

04:06.414 --> 04:07.415
BUT YOU WERE BUSY.

04:07.448 --> 04:08.682
- THEY'RE TALKING RAPE.

04:08.716 --> 04:09.917
WHERE'S THIS COMING FROM?

04:09.950 --> 04:11.852
- GIRL NAMED HEATHER RIGGS.

04:11.885 --> 04:13.754
- HEATHER WHO?

04:13.787 --> 04:17.425
- SHE LOOK FAMILIAR?

04:23.897 --> 04:25.599
- YEAH.

04:28.035 --> 04:30.003
YEAH, I THOUGHT HER NAME
WAS BROOKLYN.

04:30.037 --> 04:32.740
SHE WAS A WORKING GIRL.

04:32.773 --> 04:34.675
WHAT HAPPENED?

04:34.708 --> 04:37.411
SHE GET ARRESTED?
SHE TRY TO MAKE A DEAL?

04:37.445 --> 04:39.012
- SHE CAME IN
OF HER OWN ACCORD.

04:39.046 --> 04:40.881
- RIGHT BEFORE I TESTIFY
AGAINST GANZEL?

04:40.914 --> 04:42.583
- WELL, SHE SAID SHE NEVER
WORKED FOR GANZEL.

04:42.616 --> 04:45.419
- YEAH, SHE DIDN'T.

04:45.453 --> 04:46.954
'CAUSE BEFORE THAT,

04:46.987 --> 04:49.557
SOME, UM, SMALL TIME PIMP,

04:49.590 --> 04:51.425
FRENCH GUY, UM...

04:51.459 --> 04:52.826
ANDRE LAROUCHE.

04:52.860 --> 04:55.829
TOTAL SLEAZEBAG.
HE GOT PUT AWAY.

04:55.863 --> 04:57.931
- WELL, MS. RIGGS CLAIMS
SHE WAS FORCED INTO HOOKING,

04:57.965 --> 05:00.033
AND LAROUCHE HAD YOU
BREAK HER IN.

05:00.067 --> 05:04.372
- SHE'S LYING.

05:04.405 --> 05:06.674
AND YOU PASSED ON THE REPORT
TO IAB?

05:06.707 --> 05:08.476
- BRIAN...

05:08.509 --> 05:10.511
YOU KNOW WE HAD NO CHOICE.

05:10.544 --> 05:13.046
- YEAH, RIGHT.

05:13.080 --> 05:14.548
[chair clattering]

05:18.519 --> 05:20.354
- CASSIDY, WHAT'S UP, MAN?

05:20.388 --> 05:22.490
- JUST STOPPED BY FOR BREAKFAST.

05:22.523 --> 05:23.524
- CASSIDY.

05:23.557 --> 05:24.958
- HEY, LIV.
- HEY.

05:24.992 --> 05:28.729
- LONG TIME, NO SEE.
- YEAH, GOOD TO SEE YOU.

05:32.099 --> 05:33.734
- ARE WE MISSING SOMETHING HERE?

05:33.767 --> 05:35.903
- YOU CHILDREN DO NOT NEED
TO KNOW.

05:35.936 --> 05:38.972
- MM.

05:39.006 --> 05:40.408
- NICK, WHAT'S GOING ON?

05:40.441 --> 05:41.409
- YOU SHOULD ASK HIM.

05:41.442 --> 05:43.477
[metallic rattling]

05:43.511 --> 05:44.712
- OKAY.

05:44.745 --> 05:46.414
- REALLY?

05:46.447 --> 05:47.881
YOU AND CASSIDY.

05:47.915 --> 05:49.417
- "A," I DIDN'T TELL YOU,

05:49.450 --> 05:51.685
BECAUSE IT'S NONE
OF YOUR BUSINESS.

05:51.719 --> 05:53.954
AND, "B," IT'S NOT
THAT BIG OF A DEAL.

05:53.987 --> 05:55.756
AND "C," NICK,
I DIDN'T TELL YOU,

05:55.789 --> 05:57.991
BECAUSE I DIDN'T
WANT THIS.

06:03.864 --> 06:06.734
- JUST A LYNCH MOB
ORGANIZED BY GANZEL.

06:06.767 --> 06:08.769
HE GAVE AMARO THE ROPE.

06:08.802 --> 06:10.003
- OKAY, HOW ABOUT WE BE

06:10.037 --> 06:13.641
A LITTLE MORE SPECIFIC
THAN THAT.

06:13.674 --> 06:16.910
- I'M BEING FRAMED FOR RAPE.

06:16.944 --> 06:20.648
- RAPE?
- YEAH.

06:20.681 --> 06:22.115
- WHEN?

06:22.149 --> 06:23.484
WHO?

06:23.517 --> 06:25.486
- I GOTTA SAY, LIV,

06:25.519 --> 06:28.822
I THINK YOU'RE ASKING
THE WRONG QUESTIONS HERE.

06:28.856 --> 06:31.492
- OKAY.

06:31.525 --> 06:34.895
OKAY, SO HOW 'BOUT YOU TELL ME
WHAT I SHOULD ASK?

06:38.499 --> 06:40.634
- INTERNAL AFFAIRS?
REALLY?

06:40.668 --> 06:42.002
GOOD GOD.

06:42.035 --> 06:44.505
- BARBA SAYS
THAT IF CASSIDY WAS FRAMED,

06:44.538 --> 06:46.840
IAB WILL FIGURE IT OUT.

06:46.874 --> 06:48.642
- YOU KIDDIN' ME?
IAB?

06:48.676 --> 06:50.043
THEY MAKE FRAMES,
THEY DON'T BREAK 'EM.

06:50.077 --> 06:51.645
- I MEAN, YOU TWO KNOW HIM.

06:51.679 --> 06:53.013
ANY WAY HE'S GOOD FOR THIS?
- NO.

06:53.046 --> 06:54.882
BUT HE'S NOT GOOD
AT DEFENDING HIMSELF,

06:54.915 --> 06:56.116
AND WE HAVE
TO LOOK INTO THIS.

06:56.149 --> 06:57.651
- DISCREETLY, OF COURSE.

06:57.685 --> 07:00.588
WE CANNOT TALK TO THE VIC.

07:00.621 --> 07:02.055
- SO WE TALK
TO THE PEOPLE THAT KNOW HER.

07:02.089 --> 07:04.091
- WELL, SHE DID MENTION A JOB.

07:04.124 --> 07:05.759
- LEGIT?

07:05.793 --> 07:06.927
- SHE TEACHES
AT A POLE DANCING STUDIO,

07:06.960 --> 07:08.028
EAST VILLAGE.

07:08.061 --> 07:09.697
COME ON, FIN.

07:09.730 --> 07:11.465
LET'S WORK ON OUR TECHNIQUE.

07:13.734 --> 07:16.470
[dance music]
- ENGAGE YOUR CORE.

07:16.504 --> 07:17.905
PLACE THE SECOND HAND.

07:17.938 --> 07:19.139
LEG AROUND.

07:19.172 --> 07:23.777
AND SPIN.

07:23.811 --> 07:26.547
- SOMETHING IS VERY WRONG
ABOUT THIS.

07:26.580 --> 07:28.482
- BEATS JOGGING, I GUESS.

07:28.516 --> 07:30.150
- I'M BOBBY NAVARRO.
YOU WANTED TO SEE THE MANAGER?

07:30.183 --> 07:32.520
- YEAH, WE ACTUALLY WANTED
TO TALK TO YOU

07:32.553 --> 07:34.154
ABOUT ONE OF YOUR INSTRUCTORS,
HEATHER RIGGS.

07:34.187 --> 07:36.524
- HEATHER? GOOD PEOPLE.
WHAT ABOUT HER?

07:36.557 --> 07:37.891
- JUST A ROUTINE
BACKGROUND CHECK.

07:37.925 --> 07:39.627
HOW LONG
HAS SHE WORKED HERE?

07:39.660 --> 07:40.894
- ABOUT A YEAR.

07:40.928 --> 07:41.929
SHE'S VERY POPULAR.

07:41.962 --> 07:43.096
- IS SHE RELIABLE?

07:43.130 --> 07:45.533
- VERY.
WHAT'S THIS ABOUT?

07:45.566 --> 07:46.800
- HEATHER HAVE
ANY MONEY PROBLEMS?

07:46.834 --> 07:48.836
- NOT THAT I KNOW OF.

07:48.869 --> 07:50.671
SHE DOES PRETTY WELL HERE,
HAS GOT HER OWN FOLLOWING.

07:50.704 --> 07:53.206
- WHAT ABOUT HER PERSONAL LIFE?
BOYFRIEND?

07:53.240 --> 07:54.808
ANY TROUBLE THERE?

07:54.842 --> 07:56.043
- LOOK, WE'RE MANAGER
AND EMPLOYEE.

07:56.076 --> 07:57.645
I TRUST HER COMPLETELY.

07:57.678 --> 07:59.079
BUT SINCE YOU'RE
NOT TELLING ME WHAT'S GOING ON,

07:59.112 --> 08:01.048
I'M NOT SURE
IF I TRUST YOU SO MUCH.

08:01.081 --> 08:02.883
EXCUSE ME.

08:02.916 --> 08:04.718
- DEFENSIVE?

08:04.752 --> 08:06.654
- MORE LIKE OFFENSIVE.

08:06.687 --> 08:08.155
IF HEATHER'S SO POPULAR,

08:08.188 --> 08:09.757
HOW COME SHE ONLY TEACHES HERE
TWICE A WEEK?

08:09.790 --> 08:14.562
I MEAN, ALL THESE OTHER CHICKS
HAVE FOUR CLASSES A DAY.

08:14.595 --> 08:18.065
IT LOOKS LIKE HEATHER DOES
A LITTLE PRIVATE POLE DANCING

08:18.098 --> 08:20.067
FOR THE MANAGER,
BOBBY NAVARRO.

08:20.100 --> 08:21.569
I MEAN,
THERE'S NO PHOTOS OF HIM

08:21.602 --> 08:23.103
ON ANY
OF HER SOCIAL MEDIA PAGES,

08:23.136 --> 08:24.738
BUT, I MEAN, LOOK AT
THE OTHER INSTRUCTORS' PAGES.

08:24.772 --> 08:25.839
THEY'RE ALL OVER HIM.

08:25.873 --> 08:27.174
- YEAH, AND EACH OTHER.

08:27.207 --> 08:28.642
I WONDER
IF SHE'S EMPLOYEE OF THE MONTH.

08:28.676 --> 08:29.777
- [laughs] YEAH.

08:29.810 --> 08:31.111
- SO THE MANAGER,
WHAT DO WE HAVE?

08:31.144 --> 08:33.180
- HE HAS CONVICTIONS
FOR SHOPLIFTING,

08:33.213 --> 08:35.248
POSSESSION,
AND CHECK FRAUD.

08:35.282 --> 08:36.249
- PLUS HE WAS PICKED UP
ON A WIRETAP

08:36.283 --> 08:37.585
WITH A CHINATOWN BOOKIE.

08:37.618 --> 08:39.219
HE'S A CHRONIC GAMBLER,
WHO LOSES, SO...

08:39.252 --> 08:40.788
- WELL, THAT'S REDUNDANT.

08:40.821 --> 08:42.289
- THANK YOU, BUT ACCORDING
TO THE TAP RIGHT NOW,

08:42.322 --> 08:43.924
HE'S DOWN ABOUT 20 LARGE.

08:43.957 --> 08:45.659
- AND BACK
IN HIS CHECK FRAUD DAYS,

08:45.693 --> 08:47.761
HE MADE FAKE I.D.s.

08:47.795 --> 08:49.630
ONE WAS TERRY MATTHEWS.

08:49.663 --> 08:50.798
THE OTHER WAS LEONARD HOROWITZ.

08:50.831 --> 08:52.132
- OKAY, SO HE'S A BAD GUY.

08:52.165 --> 08:53.734
WHAT'S THIS GOT
TO DO WITH HEATHER?

08:53.767 --> 08:55.302
- WELL, CHECK THIS OUT.

08:55.335 --> 08:58.138
THIS IS THE LIST OF GANZEL'S
VISITORS UP AT RIKERS.

08:58.171 --> 08:59.707
CHECK OUT THE LAST NAME.

08:59.740 --> 09:01.575
TERRY MATTHEWS.

09:01.609 --> 09:02.776
- HOLD ON.

09:02.810 --> 09:04.845
HEATHER'S BOYFRIEND
VISITED GANZEL?

09:04.878 --> 09:06.680
WHEN WAS THIS?

09:06.714 --> 09:08.682
- TWO DAYS
BEFORE SHE CAME HERE.

09:08.716 --> 09:09.950
- ALL RIGHT,
SO SCUM KNOWS SCUM.

09:09.983 --> 09:11.685
- GANZEL PAID HIM

09:11.719 --> 09:14.187
TO GET HIS GIRLFRIEND
TO ACCUSE CASSIDY.

09:14.221 --> 09:16.757
- SEE? PARANOIA.
ANYONE CAN PLAY.

09:16.790 --> 09:17.825
I'LL TELL BARBA
THE CONNECTION.

09:17.858 --> 09:20.160
- I HAVE TO TALK
TO BARBA ANYWAY.

09:20.193 --> 09:22.663
- OKAY.

09:22.696 --> 09:25.899
- LIV, YOU WANT BACKUP?

09:25.933 --> 09:29.002
- FOR THE RECORD,
THIS IS OFF THE RECORD.

09:29.036 --> 09:30.237
THIS ISN'T YOUR CASE.

09:30.270 --> 09:32.706
- AH, DULY NOTED,
BUT IT TURNS OUT

09:32.740 --> 09:34.307
THAT OUR ALLEGED VICTIM,
HEATHER RIGGS,

09:34.341 --> 09:36.610
HAS A BOYFRIEND NAMED B--

09:36.644 --> 09:37.678
- BOBBY NAVARRO,
WHO VISITED GANZEL ON RIKERS

09:37.711 --> 09:38.979
THREE DAYS AGO.

09:39.012 --> 09:40.614
IAB KNOWS
HOW TO INVESTIGATE TOO.

09:40.648 --> 09:42.215
- GREAT, SO YOU KNOW.

09:42.249 --> 09:44.351
- NAVARRO HEARS HIS GIRLFRIEND
MET CASSIDY BACK IN THE DAY,

09:44.384 --> 09:45.986
HE KNOWS GANZEL'S
ABOUT TO GO TO TRIAL,

09:46.019 --> 09:47.721
SO HE MIDDLES A DEAL
FOR HEATHER TO SMEAR CASSIDY.

09:47.755 --> 09:49.022
- SO IT'S A CROCK.

09:49.056 --> 09:50.624
CASE CLOSED.

09:50.658 --> 09:51.759
- JUST BECAUSE NAVARRO
SAW AN OPPORTUNITY

09:51.792 --> 09:53.093
TO CASH IN
ON HEATHER'S STORY,

09:53.126 --> 09:55.028
DOESN'T MEAN
IT ISN'T TRUE.

09:55.062 --> 09:56.897
- IT DOES CAST
REASONABLE DOUBT.

09:56.930 --> 09:59.099
- SO FAR, ANY MONEY
CHANGING HANDS IS OFF THE BOOKS.

09:59.132 --> 10:00.768
WE CAN'T FIND IT.

10:00.801 --> 10:02.703
- WHAT, YOU THINK GANZEL PAYS
BY CHECK?

10:02.736 --> 10:03.937
- WE HAVE LOOKED, AND HARD.

10:03.971 --> 10:05.706
AND THERE'S MORE.

10:05.739 --> 10:07.240
HEATHER'S FORMER PIMP, ANDRE,
CONFIRMS

10:07.274 --> 10:08.709
THAT HE SENT HER TO CASSIDY.

10:08.742 --> 10:10.010
- OH, THAT'S A SHOCK.

10:10.043 --> 10:12.780
DID ANDRE GET TIME
OFF HIS SENTENCE FOR THAT?

10:12.813 --> 10:14.848
- AND ONE
OF HIS FORMER PROSTITUTES,

10:14.882 --> 10:16.283
NOW REFORMED,

10:16.316 --> 10:18.652
SWEARS THAT SHE SAW HEATHER GO
INTO THE BEDROOM

10:18.686 --> 10:20.187
WITH CASSIDY
FOR TWO HOURS.

10:20.220 --> 10:23.791
PLUS, HEATHER HAS DESCRIBED
IN GREAT DETAIL

10:23.824 --> 10:25.959
A SCAR ON CASSIDY'S
INNER THIGH.

10:25.993 --> 10:29.997
I'M GETTING A WARRANT
FOR A PHYSICAL EXAMINATION.

10:33.100 --> 10:36.770
- WELL, SAVE YOURSELF
THE TROUBLE.

10:36.804 --> 10:39.773
UH, HIS...LEFT INNER THIGH,

10:39.807 --> 10:42.843
UM...

10:42.876 --> 10:46.947
CASSIDY WAS KNIFED BY A DRUNK
WHEN HE WAS A ROOKIE.

10:46.980 --> 10:49.382
THAT'S THE OTHER THING THAT
I WANTED TO TALK TO YOU ABOUT.

10:49.416 --> 10:53.153
- AH.

10:53.186 --> 10:54.822
CURRENT RELATIONSHIP OR PAST?

10:54.855 --> 10:56.690
- BOTH.

10:56.724 --> 10:59.192
WITH A 13-YEAR GAP.

10:59.226 --> 11:01.028
- SO YOU'RE
NOT ENTIRELY OBJECTIVE.

11:01.061 --> 11:02.896
- THAT'S NOT TRUE.

11:02.930 --> 11:04.164
- DETECTIVE AMARO.

11:04.197 --> 11:06.033
YOU TALKED
TO THE COMPLAINANT.

11:06.066 --> 11:10.771
WAS SHE CREDIBLE?

11:10.804 --> 11:11.872
- YEAH, SHE WAS.

11:11.905 --> 11:14.875
