HE HAS SLEPT WITH PROSTITUTES

11:21.048 --> 11:22.315
ON THE JOB BEFORE.

11:22.349 --> 11:23.917
- YES, I REMEMBER, THANK YOU.

11:23.951 --> 11:25.052
- [sighs]

11:25.085 --> 11:27.087
A D.A. FROM WESTCHESTER
IS COMING IN

11:27.120 --> 11:29.256
TO RUN THE TRIAL.

11:29.289 --> 11:31.759
- THE TRIAL?
- WE'RE ON A FAST TRACK.

11:31.792 --> 11:35.362
WE CAN'T APPEAR
TO BE PROTECTING OUR OWN.

11:35.395 --> 11:39.767
IAB DETECTIVES ARE
ARRESTING CASSIDY RIGHT NOW.

11:52.479 --> 11:52.946
.

11:52.980 --> 11:53.881
- I'M NOT GUILTY.
- NOT GUILTY, YOUR HONOR.

11:55.482 --> 11:56.850
- PEOPLE ON BAIL?
- REMAND.

11:56.884 --> 11:58.451
THE DEFENDANT WORKED UNDERCOVER
FOR YEARS.

11:58.485 --> 12:00.220
WE BELIEVE HE MAY HAVE
HIDDEN FINANCIAL RESOURCES.

12:00.253 --> 12:03.056
