GIVES HIM MOTIVE TO FLEE.

12:03.090 --> 12:05.292
- DETECTIVE CASSIDY
IS A DECORATED OFFICER

12:05.325 --> 12:06.493
WITH NO FINANCIAL RESOURCES,

12:06.526 --> 12:08.361
NOT TO MENTION NO MOTIVATION,

12:08.395 --> 12:10.363
SINCE THE CHARGE IS BASELESS.

12:10.397 --> 12:12.432
- WE WOULDN'T BE HERE
IF IT WAS BASELESS, YOUR HONOR.

12:12.465 --> 12:14.534
- THE COURT WELCOMES
A.D.A. DEREK STRAUSS

12:14.567 --> 12:16.303
FROM WESTCHESTER COUNTY

12:16.336 --> 12:18.939
