NOT ESPECIALLY USEFUL REMARK.

12:18.972 --> 12:21.408
THE DEFENDANT IS RELEASED
ON HIS OWN RECOGNIZANCE.

12:21.441 --> 12:23.944
HE WILL SURRENDER HIS PASSPORT
AND REPORT IN DAILY.

12:23.977 --> 12:25.312
- YOUR HONOR--

12:25.345 --> 12:26.546
