MR. STRAUSS.

12:26.579 --> 12:28.548
[gavel bangs]
- SERIOUSLY, STRAUSS?

12:28.581 --> 12:30.283
"HIDDEN FINANCIAL RESOURCES"?

12:30.317 --> 12:31.551
