ON A UNI'S SALARY

12:31.584 --> 12:33.787
FOR SIX MONTHS, ALL RIGHT?

12:33.821 --> 12:36.223
- TAKE IT EASY, TAKE IT EASY.
SMALL BATTLE WON:

12:36.256 --> 12:37.490
BIG WAR TO COME.

12:37.524 --> 12:42.262
DETECTIVE, YOU ARE
A VISION TODAY.

12:42.295 --> 12:44.164
- LIV.

12:44.197 --> 12:46.199
- [under breath]
HEY.

12:46.233 --> 12:47.801
HEATHER'S STICKING
BY HER STORY.

12:47.835 --> 12:50.070
TWO WITNESSES PUT YOU
IN THAT BEDROOM WITH HER,

12:50.103 --> 12:52.840
AND SHE DESCRIBED
THE SCAR ON YOUR LEG.

12:52.873 --> 12:54.174
THAT ONE.

12:54.207 --> 12:56.343
SEE THE PROBLEM?

12:56.376 --> 12:58.011
- NOTHIN' HAPPENED.

12:58.045 --> 12:59.312
- SO YOU WEREN'T
IN THAT BEDROOM WITH HER

12:59.346 --> 13:00.848
FOR TWO HOURS?

13:00.881 --> 13:02.482
