BUT NOTHING HAPPENED.

13:02.515 --> 13:03.550
- SO HOW DOES SHE KNOW
ABOUT THE SCAR ON YOUR LEG?

13:03.583 --> 13:05.152
- I DON'T KNOW.

13:05.185 --> 13:06.453
A MILLION WAYS.

13:06.486 --> 13:09.522
IT'S NOT A STATE SECRET, LIV.

13:09.556 --> 13:11.024
HEY, LOOK!

13:11.058 --> 13:12.826
I DIDN'T DO THIS.

13:12.860 --> 13:17.064
- [sighs]

13:17.097 --> 13:18.465
SO WHAT HAPPENED
IN THAT BEDROOM?

13:18.498 --> 13:21.902
- THIS PIMP WAS
A REAL PIECE OF CRAP, OKAY?

13:21.935 --> 13:23.436
I KNEW SHE DIDN'T WANT
TO BE THERE.

13:23.470 --> 13:25.939
I COULDN'T BLOW MY COVER.

13:25.973 --> 13:27.574
SO I JUST MADE UP AN EXCUSE

13:27.607 --> 13:29.409
AND WENT
TO THE BACK BEDROOM,

13:29.442 --> 13:33.080
AND WE JUST TALKED.

13:33.113 --> 13:34.347
- OKAY.

13:34.381 --> 13:36.116
- OKAY, WHAT?

13:36.149 --> 13:38.085
YOU DO BELIEVE ME?

13:38.118 --> 13:41.221
- OF COURSE I DO.

13:44.524 --> 13:46.960
- I WAS 17.

13:46.994 --> 13:49.496
I RAN AWAY FROM HOME.

13:49.529 --> 13:51.364
I WANTED TO BE AN ACTRESS.

13:51.398 --> 13:54.434
THEN I MET ANDRE.

13:54.467 --> 13:56.503
HE SAID HE COULD HELP.
- DID HE HELP?

13:56.536 --> 14:00.607
- NO, HE LOCKED ME IN
AN APARTMENT WITH OTHER GIRLS...

14:00.640 --> 14:02.609
TOOK AWAY MY CLOTHES.

14:02.642 --> 14:05.012
HE MADE US HAVE SEX
WITH STRANGERS.

14:05.045 --> 14:07.014
- THOSE STRANGERS...

14:07.047 --> 14:09.516
HE MADE YOU HAVE SEX WITH,

14:09.549 --> 14:10.583
DO YOU SEE
ONE OF THEM HERE?

14:10.617 --> 14:13.353
- YES.

14:13.386 --> 14:14.621
HIM.

14:14.654 --> 14:16.189
- LET THE RECORD REFLECT

14:16.223 --> 14:18.391
SHE'S POINTING
AT THE DEFENDANT BRIAN CASSIDY.

14:18.425 --> 14:20.293
- HE SAID HIS NAME WAS RICK.

14:20.327 --> 14:22.529
I THOUGHT HE WAS
A FRIEND OF ANDRE'S.

14:22.562 --> 14:25.232
ANDRE TOLD HIM
THAT I WAS NEW.

14:25.265 --> 14:27.467
[voice trembles] AND THAT
HE SHOULD HELP BREAK ME IN.

14:27.500 --> 14:30.037
- AND IS THAT
WHEN DETECTIVE CASSIDY TOOK YOU

14:30.070 --> 14:32.372
INTO THE BEDROOM?

14:32.405 --> 14:37.144
- [crying] I DIDN'T KNOW
HE WAS A DETECTIVE.

14:37.177 --> 14:39.079
[sobbing]
WE HAD SEX.

14:39.112 --> 14:40.647
I DIDN'T WANT TO.

14:40.680 --> 14:42.349
HE KNEW I DIDN'T WANT TO.

14:42.382 --> 14:46.653
I CRIED THE WHOLE TIME.

14:46.686 --> 14:49.556
- ARE YOU SURE
THE MAN YOU WERE WITH...

14:49.589 --> 14:52.092
IS THE DEFENDANT?

14:52.125 --> 14:54.561
- YES.

14:54.594 --> 14:58.298
I SAW THE SCAR NEXT TO HIS...

14:58.331 --> 15:00.567
HIS BUSINESS.
[sniffles]

15:00.600 --> 15:04.204
- THANK YOU.

15:06.673 --> 15:08.508
- MS. RIGGS.

15:08.541 --> 15:11.244
WHAT WOULD ANDRE HAVE DONE

15:11.278 --> 15:14.081
IF HE'D KNOWN
YOU DIDN'T HAVE SEX

15:14.114 --> 15:16.516
WITH DETECTIVE CASSIDY?

15:16.549 --> 15:18.251
- HE'D HAVE BEATEN ME.

15:18.285 --> 15:22.089
HE USED SACKS OF ORANGES
SO THE BRUISES WOULDN'T SHOW.

15:22.122 --> 15:25.558
- SO IF DETECTIVE CASSIDY WANTED
TO PROTECT YOU,

15:25.592 --> 15:27.594
HE WOULD HAVE KEPT YOU
IN THAT ROOM

15:27.627 --> 15:28.728
FOR A WHILE.

15:28.761 --> 15:31.264
- PROTECT ME?

15:31.298 --> 15:32.532
NOBODY PROTECTED ME.

15:32.565 --> 15:34.201
- EVEN NOW...

15:34.234 --> 15:37.704
IS ANYONE PROTECTING YOU?

15:37.737 --> 15:39.472
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

15:39.506 --> 15:41.708
- DO YOU HAVE A BOYFRIEND NAMED
BOBBY NAVARRO?

15:41.741 --> 15:43.010
- YES.

15:43.043 --> 15:45.178
- ARE YOU AWARE

15:45.212 --> 15:46.679
HE VISITED BART GANZEL
IN PRISON?

15:46.713 --> 15:48.615
THAT HE ATTEMPTED
TO GET MONEY

15:48.648 --> 15:51.051
IN EXCHANGE
FOR YOUR TESTIMONY

15:51.084 --> 15:52.585
AGAINST DETECTIVE CASSIDY?

15:52.619 --> 15:56.189
- I DIDN'T KNOW
THAT HE DID THAT UNTIL AFTER.

15:56.223 --> 15:58.458
AND--AND HE DIDN'T GET MONEY.

15:58.491 --> 16:00.727
- BUT YOU ARE PLANNING ON
CASHING IN ON THIS,

16:00.760 --> 16:02.195
AREN'T YOU?

16:02.229 --> 16:03.763
HAVEN'T YOU HIRED AN ATTORNEY

16:03.796 --> 16:05.698
TO SUE THE CITY FOR DAMAGES?

16:05.732 --> 16:07.234
- I WAS RAPED!

16:07.267 --> 16:10.970
SOMEBODY OUGHT
TO BE RESPONSIBLE!

16:12.705 --> 16:15.375
- I'M AN OUTREACH COUNSELOR

16:15.408 --> 16:19.079
WITH AN ORGANIZATION
THAT HELPS FORMER SEX WORKERS

16:19.112 --> 16:20.780
AND TRAFFICKED WOMEN.

16:20.813 --> 16:22.549
- AND HOW DID YOU GET
INTO THIS FIELD?

16:22.582 --> 16:24.384
- PERSONAL EXPERIENCE.

16:24.417 --> 16:26.219
I WAS A TRAFFICKED SEX WORKER.

16:26.253 --> 16:28.421
FOR A PIMP
NAMED ANDRE LAROUCHE.

16:28.455 --> 16:30.623
- THE SAME PIMP
WHO EMPLOYED HEATHER RIGGS.

16:30.657 --> 16:31.791
- YES.

16:31.824 --> 16:34.261
HEATHER WAS NEW.

16:34.294 --> 16:37.730
AND TERRIFIED.

16:37.764 --> 16:42.302
ANDRE ORDERED HER
INTO A BEDROOM WITH HIM.

16:42.335 --> 16:45.205
THEY WERE IN THERE TOGETHER
FOR AT LEAST TWO HOURS.

16:45.238 --> 16:47.340
- THANK YOU.

16:47.374 --> 16:50.410
- DID YOU SEE MS. RIGGS
AND DETECTIVE CASSIDY

16:50.443 --> 16:51.678
HAVING SEX?

16:51.711 --> 16:52.712
- NO.

16:52.745 --> 16:54.214
THE DOOR TO THE ROOM
WAS CLOSED.

16:54.247 --> 16:56.516
- DID YOU HEAR THEM?
- NO.

16:56.549 --> 16:58.185
I WAS ASSIGNED TO ANOTHER ROOM
A FEW MINUTES LATER.

16:58.218 --> 17:01.221
- DID YOU HEAR
THE ALLEGED COMMENT

17:01.254 --> 17:03.356
YOUR PIMP MADE
TO DETECTIVE CASSIDY--

17:03.390 --> 17:07.160
THAT HE WANTED HIM
TO "BREAK MS. RIGGS IN"?

17:07.194 --> 17:08.395
- I DIDN'T.

17:08.428 --> 17:11.231
- BUT THAT ALLEGED COMMENT,

17:11.264 --> 17:14.601
WHICH APPARENTLY NOBODY
BUT MS. RIGGS HEARD,

17:14.634 --> 17:15.702
IS THE ONLY WAY

17:15.735 --> 17:17.804
DETECTIVE CASSIDY
WOULD HAVE KNOWN

17:17.837 --> 17:19.272
SHE WASN'T WILLING?

17:19.306 --> 17:20.740
- THE ONLY WAY?

17:20.773 --> 17:23.743
WE WEREN'T GIRLS
GOING OUT WITH GUYS

17:23.776 --> 17:24.844
TO DINNER AND A MOVIE,

17:24.877 --> 17:26.713
AND THEN, MAYBE,
IF WE LIKED THEM,

17:26.746 --> 17:28.815
THEY'D GET LUCKY.

17:28.848 --> 17:31.684
WE WERE LOCKED IN A ROOM.

17:31.718 --> 17:35.388
WE HAD DOG COLLARS
AROUND OUR NECKS.

17:35.422 --> 17:37.457
I'D SAY IT'S
PRETTY DAMN OBVIOUS

17:37.490 --> 17:41.528
SHE WASN'T WILLING.

17:41.561 --> 17:44.431
- SHE WAS TELLING THE TRUTH.

17:44.464 --> 17:46.766
SHE JUST DOESN'T KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED IN THAT ROOM.

17:46.799 --> 17:48.768
- WELL, THAT'S THE PROBLEM
WITH SEX CRIMES:

17:48.801 --> 17:51.638
NO ONE EVER DOES, EXCEPT
THE PEOPLE THAT WERE THERE,

17:51.671 --> 17:52.872
AND THEY ALWAYS DISAGREE.

17:52.905 --> 17:54.874
- YOU WANT
TO TAKE THE STAND, JOHN?

17:54.907 --> 17:56.343
- I ALREADY ASKED YOUR LAWYER.

17:56.376 --> 17:57.844
HE FEELS THAT,
BECAUSE YOU AND I WERE PARTNERS,

17:57.877 --> 18:00.113
THAT THE JURY'D PERCEIVE ME
AS BEING BIASED,

18:00.147 --> 18:01.714
WHICH, OF COURSE,
I WOULD BE.

18:01.748 --> 18:03.183
- WHAT ABOUT YOUR PAL, AMARO?

18:03.216 --> 18:04.817
THE D.A.'S CALLING HIM
AS A WITNESS.

18:04.851 --> 18:06.186
- HE'S NOT IN YOUR FAN CLUB,

18:06.219 --> 18:07.754
BUT HE CAUGHT
HEATHER'S STATEMENT,

18:07.787 --> 18:09.756
SO THAT'S ALL
THEY'RE GONNA ASK HIM ABOUT.

18:09.789 --> 18:12.825
- YOU KNOW HE'S GONNA TRY TO
THROW ME UNDER THE BUS, RIGHT?

18:12.859 --> 18:14.327
- HE WAS UNDERCOVER FOR YEARS.

18:14.361 --> 18:15.862
HE KNOWS EXACTLY
WHAT YOU'VE BEEN GOING THROUGH.

18:15.895 --> 18:18.131
OKAY?

18:20.767 --> 18:22.835
- DETECTIVE, WHEN YOU
FIRST QUESTIONED THE DEFENDANT

18:22.869 --> 18:24.571
ABOUT MS. RIGGS,

18:24.604 --> 18:26.839
HOW DID HE DESCRIBE
HIS RELATIONSHIP WITH HER?

18:26.873 --> 18:28.675
- HE SAID
HE RECOGNIZED HER PICTURE

18:28.708 --> 18:30.177
AND REMEMBERED MEETING HER.

18:30.210 --> 18:31.744
- WOULD YOU SAY
HE WAS FORTHCOMING?

18:31.778 --> 18:32.812
- HE WAS FORTHRIGHT
IN HIS ANGER

18:32.845 --> 18:34.247
AND SAID
HE WAS BEING SET UP

18:34.281 --> 18:35.815
AND THAT NOTHING
HAD HAPPENED.

18:35.848 --> 18:38.218
- SO HE NEVER TOLD YOU
HE WENT INTO A BEDROOM

18:38.251 --> 18:40.920
WITH MS. RIGGS
FOR TWO HOURS?

18:40.953 --> 18:43.156
- NO, HE DIDN'T.
- YOU'VE WORKED UNDERCOVER,

18:43.190 --> 18:44.491
HAVEN'T YOU, DETECTIVE?

18:44.524 --> 18:46.793
- YES, ON AND OFF
FOR EIGHT YEARS.

18:46.826 --> 18:50.530
- YOU EVER GO INTO A BEDROOM
ALONE WITH A SEX SLAVE?

18:52.799 --> 18:54.901
- NO.

18:54.934 --> 18:57.904
- YOU WERE TRAINED TO AVOID
COMPROMISING SITUATIONS?

18:57.937 --> 19:00.673
- AS OFTEN AS POSSIBLE,
YEAH, BUT EVERY SITUA--

19:00.707 --> 19:02.809
- SO GOING INTO A BEDROOM ALONE
WITH A PROSTITUTE,

19:02.842 --> 19:07.680
THAT WOULD BE AN INVITATION
TO COMMIT A CRIME?

19:07.714 --> 19:09.749
- ISN'T THAT A HYPOTHETICAL?

19:09.782 --> 19:10.950
- WELL, IT'S
AN UNLAWFUL SITUATION:

19:10.983 --> 19:12.752
YES OR NO?

19:12.785 --> 19:14.421
- YES, BUT AGAIN,

19:14.454 --> 19:15.888
I CAN'T PUT MYSELF
IN ANOTHER UC'S POSITION.

19:15.922 --> 19:17.357
- I'M NOT ASKING YOU TO.

19:17.390 --> 19:18.825
I'M ASKING,
WHAT WOULD YOU DO

19:18.858 --> 19:19.926
IF A SEX TRAFFICKER
YOU WERE INVESTIGATING

19:19.959 --> 19:21.428
OFFERED YOU THE SERVICES

19:21.461 --> 19:25.932
OF A SEMI-NAKED WOMAN
WEARING A DOG COLLAR?

19:25.965 --> 19:26.799
- I WOULD DECLINE.

19:26.833 --> 19:28.768
- UNDER ALL CIRCUMSTANCES?

19:28.801 --> 19:31.271
- YES.

19:31.304 --> 19:34.207
- THANK YOU.

19:34.241 --> 19:35.808
- CROSS, MR. QUERNS?

19:35.842 --> 19:37.644
- WHY DON'T WE TAKE THIS UP

19:37.677 --> 19:39.479
AFTER LUNCH, YOUR HONOR?

19:39.512 --> 19:40.813
- VERY WELL.

19:40.847 --> 19:42.715
COURT'S IN RECESS.
[bangs gavel]

19:45.585 --> 19:46.819
- MR. BARBA.

19:46.853 --> 19:48.288
HOW'S THE VIEW
FROM THE CHEAP SEATS?

19:48.321 --> 19:49.556
- FASCINATING.

19:49.589 --> 19:50.990
ESPECIALLY WHEN
A DEFENSE ATTORNEY

19:51.023 --> 19:52.692
ALLOWS A PROSECUTOR
TO TURN A SIMPLE FACT WITNESS

19:52.725 --> 19:54.827
INTO A CHARACTER ASSASSIN
WITHOUT OBJECTING.

19:54.861 --> 19:56.696
- MY GOD,
THAT DEFENSE ATTORNEY

19:56.729 --> 19:58.231
SOUNDS LIKE
A COMPLETE INCOMPETENT.

19:58.265 --> 19:59.499
- YES, BUT HE ISN'T.

19:59.532 --> 20:01.834
SO I WONDER WHY?
- LOVE TO CHAT.

20:01.868 --> 20:05.438
WE ONLY HAVE AN HOUR
FOR LUNCH.

20:10.042 --> 20:12.312
DETECTIVE,
IT MUST FEEL ODD

20:12.345 --> 20:15.982
TESTIFYING AGAINST
A FELLOW UNDERCOVER OFFICER.

20:16.015 --> 20:17.984
- IT'S NOT
THE MOST COMFORTABLE THING.

20:18.017 --> 20:19.419
- BECAUSE UNDERCOVER OFFICERS

20:19.452 --> 20:21.821
SHARE CERTAIN UNIQUE PRESSURES
AND EXPERIENCES,

20:21.854 --> 20:23.390
DO THEY NOT?

20:23.423 --> 20:25.492
- OBJECTION. YOUR HONOR,
WHAT'S THE RELEVANCE?

20:25.525 --> 20:27.894
- YOUR HONOR, THE PROSECUTION
QUESTIONED THIS WITNESS

20:27.927 --> 20:30.730
AT LENGTH
ABOUT UNDERCOVER OPERATIONS.

20:30.763 --> 20:32.865
THAT DOOR HAS BEEN OPENED.

20:32.899 --> 20:33.900
- SO IT HAS.

20:33.933 --> 20:35.735
YOU MAY PROCEED.

20:35.768 --> 20:37.870
- DETECTIVE,
DON'T UNDERCOVER OFFICERS

20:37.904 --> 20:40.006
SOMETIMES BREAK THE LAW

20:40.039 --> 20:42.008
IN ORDER
TO BRING DOWN MAJOR CRIMINALS?

20:42.041 --> 20:42.975
- WE'RE NOT SUPPOSED TO.

20:43.009 --> 20:44.977
- BUT IT HAPPENS.

20:45.011 --> 20:48.881
FOR EXAMPLE, HAVE YOU EVER
PARTAKEN IN ILLEGAL DRUGS?

20:48.915 --> 20:50.883
- ONCE.

20:50.917 --> 20:53.019
I WAS NEW
TO A DRUG DEALER'S ORGANIZATION.

20:53.052 --> 20:54.321
I WAS BEING TESTED.

20:54.354 --> 20:56.456
IF I REFUSED,
I MIGHT HAVE BEEN SHOT.

20:56.489 --> 20:59.826
- SO A GOOD UNDERCOVER AGENT,
LIKE YOURSELF,

20:59.859 --> 21:02.762
FINDS WAYS
TO AVOID BREAKING THE LAW.

21:02.795 --> 21:04.631
- YES, THAT'S PROTOCOL.

21:04.664 --> 21:06.533
- NOW IF YOU WERE INFILTRATING
A NEW ORGANIZATION,

21:06.566 --> 21:08.034
YOU WOULD FIND WAYS

21:08.067 --> 21:11.704
TO AVOID INAPPROPRIATE
SEXUAL RELATIONSHIPS?

21:11.738 --> 21:13.940
- YES.

21:13.973 --> 21:15.442
- ONLY IF YOUR LIFE
DEPENDED ON IT,

21:15.475 --> 21:17.510
WOULD YOU CROSS THAT LINE?

21:17.544 --> 21:20.012
- YES, BUT AGAIN, I CAN'T SPEAK
TO THE SPECIFICS OF ANOTHER--

21:20.046 --> 21:21.013
- THEN DON'T.

21:21.047 --> 21:22.949
LET'S KEEP THIS SIMPLE.

21:22.982 --> 21:26.018
DID YOU EVER HAVE INAPPROPRIATE
SEXUAL RELATIONSHIPS

21:26.052 --> 21:28.955
IN YOUR UNDERCOVER ROLE?

21:28.988 --> 21:31.090
- I NEVER SLEPT
WITH A COERCED PROSTITUTE.

21:31.123 --> 21:33.393
- DID YOU EVER SLEEP WITH ANYONE
UNDER FALSE PRETENSES?

21:33.426 --> 21:36.329
- YOUR HONOR,
THIS IS WAY OFF BASE.

21:36.363 --> 21:37.864
- MR. QUERNS,
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

21:37.897 --> 21:42.402
- ALMOST DONE,
YOUR HONOR.

21:45.838 --> 21:47.540
DETECTIVE, DO YOU RECOGNIZE

21:47.574 --> 21:48.975
THE WOMAN WHO JUST ENTERED
THE COURTROOM?

21:49.008 --> 21:50.109
- OBJECTION, YOUR HONOR.

21:50.142 --> 21:52.745
WE HAVE NO IDEA
WHO THIS WOMAN IS.

21:52.779 --> 21:55.782
- I BELIEVE DETECTIVE AMARO
CAN HELP US OUT WITH THAT.

21:55.815 --> 21:58.084
DETECTIVE, IS SHE THE SISTER
OF A DRUG KINGPIN

21:58.117 --> 22:00.387
WHOSE ORGANIZATION
YOU INFILTRATED?

22:00.420 --> 22:02.054
- OH, OBJECTION, YOUR HONOR.

22:02.088 --> 22:06.626
- HOW WELL DO YOU KNOW HER...
DETECTIVE?

22:09.028 --> 22:12.098
- I KNEW HER...

22:12.131 --> 22:13.132
VERY WELL.

22:13.165 --> 22:14.667
- OBJECTION, YOUR HONOR!

