ALL YOU CAN GET.

36:06.232 --> 36:07.733
ADDERALL FOR THE KIDS.

36:07.766 --> 36:09.368
AND WHILE YOU'RE AT IT,

36:09.401 --> 36:11.203
WHY DON'T YOU THROW
A FEW RIPPERS IN THE BAG,

36:11.237 --> 36:12.804
FOR ME AND MY OLD LADY HERE,
HMM?

36:12.838 --> 36:16.808
[slaps her bottom]

36:20.412 --> 36:23.749
[dance music]

36:23.782 --> 36:25.384
*

36:25.417 --> 36:27.386
- WHO ARE YOU TWO?

36:27.419 --> 36:29.321
- YOU KNOW MR. YEE?

36:29.355 --> 36:31.390
HE HAS TRANSFERRED YOUR DEBT
OVER TO US.

36:31.423 --> 36:32.691
- YOU GUYS ARE IN LUCK,

36:32.724 --> 36:34.326
I'M COMING
INTO SERIOUS MONEY REAL SOON.

36:34.360 --> 36:36.595
- WHAT, YOU BEEN PAYING
TWO GRAND A WEEK IN VIG?

36:36.628 --> 36:37.829
IT'S GONNA GO UP.

36:37.863 --> 36:40.299
- UNLESS YOU PAY US
THE 20 NOW.

36:40.332 --> 36:42.334
- I DON'T HAVE
THE 20 RIGHT NOW.

36:42.368 --> 36:43.869
[grunts]

36:43.902 --> 36:48.907
- THEN YOU'RE GONNA HAVE
TO WORK IT OFF.

36:48.940 --> 36:51.910
[dramatic music]

36:51.943 --> 36:59.951
*

37:15.534 --> 37:17.403
- WHO ARE YOU?
- I'M THE ONE WITH THE MONEY.

37:17.436 --> 37:18.970
YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO GIVE ME A PACKAGE.

37:19.004 --> 37:20.706
- WHERE'S THE GUY WITH
THE BULLET HOLES AND THE BLONDE?

37:20.739 --> 37:23.709
- CAN WE JUST DO THIS? LOOK.
- YOU KNOW WHAT?

37:23.742 --> 37:24.843
I DON'T KNOW WHAT THE HELL
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

37:24.876 --> 37:26.278
- WHAT?

37:26.312 --> 37:27.846
[siren whoops,
tires squeal]

37:27.879 --> 37:31.617
[sirens wail]

37:31.650 --> 37:34.720
[tires screech]

37:35.887 --> 37:37.055
- POLICE! FREEZE!

37:37.088 --> 37:38.990
- LET ME SEE THOSE HANDS!

37:39.024 --> 37:41.927
WHERE WE CAN SEE 'EM!
LET ME SEE YOUR HANDS!

37:45.831 --> 37:47.833
[handcuffs clicking]

37:51.503 --> 37:53.004
- THANK YOU.

37:53.038 --> 37:54.506
POP THE TRUNK.

37:57.476 --> 37:58.777
- GET A LOAD OF THIS.

37:58.810 --> 38:01.713
LOOKS LIKE HE'S GOT
A DRUGSTORE IN THERE.

38:01.747 --> 38:03.949
- MAN, YOU MUST HAVE
A SERIOUS HEADACHE.

38:03.982 --> 38:05.651
- SON OF A BITCH!

38:05.684 --> 38:07.653
- ALL RIGHT,
GET HIM OUTTA HERE.

38:11.923 --> 38:14.560
- THANKS, DOOM.
- OUR PLEASURE.

38:14.593 --> 38:17.028
DETECTIVE ROLLINS,
ALWAYS A TREAT.

38:17.062 --> 38:20.031
DO I WANT TO KNOW HOW YOU KNEW
THIS DEAL WAS GOING DOWN?

38:20.065 --> 38:21.933
- NOPE.
- WHAT I FIGURED.

38:21.967 --> 38:23.969
- YOU GOT THIS ONE SOLID,
RIGHT?

38:24.002 --> 38:26.405
- YEAH, HE'S GOT MAJOR WEIGHT
IN HIS TRUNK--HE'S DONE.

38:26.438 --> 38:27.873
SO'S HIS CUSTOMER.

38:27.906 --> 38:29.408
- YEAH, HIS CUSTOMER--

38:29.441 --> 38:31.977
WE'D ACTUALLY LIKE
TO, UM, BORROW HIM.

38:32.010 --> 38:34.880
- BE MY GUEST.

38:34.913 --> 38:36.948
- YOU SET ME UP, MAN.
THIS IS PAYBACK, RIGHT?

38:36.982 --> 38:38.917
- COME ON.
$10,000 CASH, MIDNIGHT.

38:38.950 --> 38:40.986
YOU'RE MEETING A MAN WITH
A TRUNK FULL OF STOLEN MEDS.

38:41.019 --> 38:42.854
- SOMEBODY ELSE IS GONNA
BE TEACHING THOSE GIRLS

38:42.888 --> 38:45.857
HOW TO POLE DANCE
FOR THE NEXT 20 YEARS.

38:45.891 --> 38:47.125
- THAT'S WHAT
THIS IS ABOUT?

38:47.158 --> 38:48.760
WHAT HEATHER SAID
ABOUT THAT COP?

38:48.794 --> 38:51.963
- WHY? YOU KNOW
SOMETHING ABOUT THAT?

38:53.899 --> 38:55.901
- I'M GUESSING
IT'S DEAL TIME.

38:55.934 --> 38:58.770
- DEPENDS ON WHAT
YOU GOT TO SAY.

39:01.607 --> 39:02.841
- [sighs]

39:02.874 --> 39:05.010
OKAY, IT DIDN'T HAPPEN.

39:05.043 --> 39:08.013
HEATHER AND I
MADE IT UP TO CASH IN.

39:09.881 --> 39:11.883
- WHAT DIDN'T HAPPEN?

39:11.917 --> 39:15.554
- HE DIDN'T RAPE HER.
HE DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.

39:15.587 --> 39:17.556
GANZEL DIDN'T GIVE ME THE MONEY,
BUT HE TOLD ME ABOUT THE SCAR.

39:17.589 --> 39:18.990
HE SAID IT WOULD
HELP HEATHER'S CASE.

39:19.024 --> 39:24.730
WE WERE GONNA SUE THE CITY.
MAKE A MILLION DOLLARS.

39:24.763 --> 39:27.032
- IS THAT WHAT HAPPENED,
HEATHER?

39:27.065 --> 39:29.735
IS THAT THE TRUTH?
- HOW MUCH TROUBLE AM I IN?

39:29.768 --> 39:31.903
- THAT'S NOT UP TO ME.

39:31.937 --> 39:37.576
BUT I NEED YOU TO TELL ME,
IS THAT WHAT HAPPENED?

39:37.609 --> 39:40.746
- YOU KNOW CASSIDY?

39:40.779 --> 39:43.615
- YEAH.

39:43.649 --> 39:46.752
I DO.

39:52.858 --> 39:55.861
- HE DIDN'T TOUCH ME.

40:00.632 --> 40:02.934
WE JUST TALKED.

40:02.968 --> 40:06.071
ABOUT DOGS.

40:06.104 --> 40:09.074
- HEATHER...

40:09.107 --> 40:13.945
I NEED TO KNOW IF ANYBODY ELSE
CAN VERIFY THIS VERSION

40:13.979 --> 40:16.915
OF YOUR STORY.

40:16.948 --> 40:18.584
- YES.

40:18.617 --> 40:22.754
YES, LATER THAT NIGHT,
I TOLD ANOTHER ONE OF THE GIRLS

40:22.788 --> 40:26.825
HOW HE DIDN'T MAKE ME--

40:26.858 --> 40:30.095
[crying]
HOW NICE HE WAS TO ME.

40:35.967 --> 40:38.904
- HEY.
- HEY.

40:38.937 --> 40:41.607
OUR LITTLE PRICK D.A.--
HE INTERVIEWED HEATHER,

40:41.640 --> 40:43.575
HEATHER'S BOYFRIEND NAVARRO,
ALSO HEATHER'S FRIEND

40:43.609 --> 40:44.876
THAT WAS THERE THAT NIGHT.

40:44.910 --> 40:46.011
HE DROPPED THE CHARGE.

40:46.044 --> 40:47.546
- SO YOU'RE FREE.

40:47.579 --> 40:49.581
- YEAH, I'M FREE
TO WORK THE NIGHT SHIFT

40:49.615 --> 40:52.017
AT BRONX COURTHOUSE.
COME ON.

40:52.050 --> 40:53.852
I THINK I'M JUST
GONNA STICK IT OUT.

40:53.885 --> 40:55.587
I'M GONNA GET MY 20.

40:55.621 --> 40:59.090
I'M DAMAGED GOODS, LIV.
- BRIAN, YOU DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.

40:59.124 --> 41:02.093
- ONCE ACCUSED,
ALWAYS UNDER SUSPICION.

41:02.127 --> 41:05.030
EVEN FROM YOU.

41:05.063 --> 41:08.567
- FROM ME?

41:08.600 --> 41:10.268
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
I BELIEVED YOU.

41:10.301 --> 41:13.905
- I WISH I COULD
BELIEVE THAT.

41:13.939 --> 41:16.241
- BRIAN, COME ON,
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

41:16.274 --> 41:17.809
OH, WHAT?
SO WE'RE OVER NOW?

41:17.843 --> 41:20.712
- I DON'T KNOW.
I DON'T KNOW.

41:24.082 --> 41:28.587
YOU WANT TO GO GET A DRINK
SOMEWHERE AND NOT TALK ABOUT IT?
